{"word":"Nazareth","slug":"nazareth","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Nazareth</b> <a href=\"#/G3478\">G3478</a> <br/> A village in Galilee.<br/> Joseph and Mary dwell at<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=2&verse=23'>Mat 2:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=1&verse=27'>Luk 1:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=1&verse=56'>Luk 1:56</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=2&verse=4'>Luk 2:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=2&verse=39'>Luk 2:39</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=2&verse=51'>Luk 2:51</a><br/> Jesus from<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=21&verse=11'>Mat 21:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=1&verse=24'>Mar 1:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=10&verse=47'>Mar 10:47</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=4&verse=34'>Luk 4:34</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=18&verse=37'>Luk 18:37</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=24&verse=19'>Luk 24:19</a><br/> People of, reject Jesus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=4&verse=30'>Luk 4:30</a><br/> Its name opprobrious (carrying a sense of disgrace)<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=1&verse=46'>Joh 1:46</a>"}]}